程序包 Model

类 Choice

java.lang.Object
Model.Choice
public class Choice extends Object
Represents a single choice in a chat response from an AI service in the Smart Finance Application. This class encapsulates the index of the choice, the message content, and the reason why the response generation finished.
版本:
1.0
作者:
Group 19
